des:
Pawcatuck North Stonington Little League Majors division games schedule by the next game number. Game times, ballfield, and opponent teams are provided. No personal information is being used within this skill and is nothing is being collected or saved. This skill is a simple aide to help parents find their teams ballfield when they arrive at the games using this new technology instead of texting and emailing the coaches. Say your team name to hear the next time, field, and opponent your team is playing. Team names are;
Silvia Landscaping
Dunkin' Donuts
North Stonington Grange
Schilke Realty
Pawcatuck Lions
